oard, or breakout in virtual rooms to get most out of your work meetings. \\n\\nDesigned to give you peace of mind: \\n• Securely collaborate with external partners for work assignments while maintaining control over your data. \\n• Store important information such as subscription passwords in a digital Safe*. \\n• Enterprise-level security and compliance you expect from Microsoft 365**. \\n\\n*Available when using Microsoft Teams with your personal account.  \\n**Commercial features of this app require a paid Microsoft 365 commercial subscription or a trial subscription of Microsoft Teams for work. If you’re not sure about your company’s subscription or the services you have access to, visit Office.com/Teams to learn more or contact your IT department. \\n\\nBy downloading Teams, you agree to the license (see aka.ms/eulateamsmobile) and privacy terms (see aka.ms/privacy). For support or feedback, email us at mtiosapp@microsoft.com. EU Contract Summary: aka.ms/EUContractSummary\",\"trackId\":1113153706,\"version\":\"4.2.0\",\"wrapperType\":\"software\",\"userRatingCount\":2073539},{\"screenshotUrls\":[\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource114/v4/64/a4/04/64a40462-434e-4232-cf52-2e6a127e0703/a439bd8d-3a63-4a78-b549-dd91f41a3eaf_1.png/392x696bb.png\",\"https://is5-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource114/v4/54/10/a0/5410a0d4-5ea6-87b2-9749-bbc0330ac556/be749099-27cd-4afe-bb72-3e496378a820_2.png/392x696bb.png\",\"https://is3-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource114/v4/92/6c/ae/926cae1b-2b71-78c6-14c4-e4a7302264ed/2382949b-dba5-4280-b491-c2a9f234deb2_3.png/392x696bb.png\",\"https://is5-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource114/v4/c0/71/e0/c071e0eb-ba97-f28e-477b-d086a43f0c97/ecda6f34-9d39-4eb2-aa1f-ffb62f86634a_4.png/392x696bb.png\",\"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/PurpleSource114/v4/d7/b2/5a/d7b25a66-423d-a976-9e0f-ac3d4bc527cf/764346d6-e747-4bb4-be13-c270527381dd_5.png/392x696bb.png\"],\"ipadScreenshotUrls\":[],\"appletvScreenshot